      "text": "Un Babele tapê par Ak-\nmixo-Kobpn/ par Puhku Mah-\njas-Weetu/ par Istrubzinatcha-\nnu/ un par Apfineekli/ ka ne-\nweens tur dsihwo.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 38,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee ruhks kohpâ ka Lau-\nwas/ un btaus ka jaunt Lau-\nwas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 39,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad tee irr eekahrseti/ tad\nzelschu es teem winnu Dschreenu\npreekscha/ un peedsirdinatchu\ntohs ka tee uhslezz/ bet tee gul-\nlehs weenn muhschtigu Meegu/\nun ne uhsniohdisees/ taka tas\nKUNGS.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 40,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es noweddischu tohs ka\nJehrus pee Kauschanas/ ka Au-\nnus ar Abscheem\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 41,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ka irr Seesaks ta us-\njemts? un tas flawehts eeksch\nwiffas Semmes ta pahrwar-\nrehts? ka irr Babele par Istrub-\nzinaschannu tappuft starp teem\nPaganeem?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 42,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Weena Juhra irr pahr\nBabeli gahjust/ un zaur winnas\nWilau Wairuma irr ta apklab-\nta tappuft.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 43,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Winnu Pilsfahfti irr poh-\nsta tappusch/ par kaltuschu tuk-\nschu Senmit/ par tahdu Sem-\nmi/ fur neveens dsihwo/ fur ne-\nweens Zilweka Behrns zaurees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 44,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un es peemekleschu to\nBellu eeksch Babeles/ un tsran-\nschu no winna Rihkles/ ko\nwiꞥſch irr eerihjis/ un tee Paga-\nri ne tezzehs wairs pee winnu/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 45,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Eita ahra manni Kan-\ndis no winnas Widdus/ un is-\nglahbeet ikweens fatwu Dwehseli\nta Karstuma deht/ tahs Bahrsi-\nbas ta KUNGA.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 46,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ka jaschu juhsfa Sirđs\nne tohp bailiga/ un juhs tsbth-\nstatees no tahs Glawas/ kastai\nSemmê taps dsirdeta. Jo Gla-\nwa nahks weend Gaddâ/un pehz\nweena Glawa ohtrâ Gaddâ/ un\nWarras-Darhs buhs tai Sem-\nimê/ weens Waldneeks prett oh-\ntru.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 47,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tapehz rangi/ tahs Dee-\nnas nahk/ tad peemekleschu es\ntohs Deewektus no Babeles/ un\nwiffa winnas Semme taps Kan-\nnâ/ un wiffi winnas Nokantee\ngullehs winnas Widdû.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 48,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un prett Babeli gawi-\nfehs Debbes un Semme/ un\nwiss/ kas eeksch tahs irraid/ jo\nno Secmeta-Puffes nahks pahr\nwinnu tee Pohstitajt/ fatka tas\nKUNGS.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 49,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ka Babele irr par\nKrittumu bijusi teem Nokan-\nteem eeksch Israeka/ ta krittihs\neeksch Babeles tee Nokantee wif-\nfas tahs Semmes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 50,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Juhs Jsglahbtee no ta\nSchbina/ eita nohst/ un ne pa-\nstahweet/ peeminneet to KUNgu\nno tahas Semmes/ un turrajt\nJerusaemi juhsa Sirđi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 51,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Mehs effam Rauna tap-\npuschi/ jo mehs effam Neewa-\nschannu\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
